⸻

Detection Objectives

These scenarios validate the visibility of common attacker actions inside a Windows Active Directory environment.

The dashboards should successfully detect:

* SSH brute force attacks
* Successful SSH authentication
* Interactive attacker activity
* Host discovery
* PowerShell execution
* Active Directory enumeration
* User account creation
* Privileged group modifications
* User account deletion

⸻

